@startuml SD_17_NotificationSystem
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - Hệ thống Thông báo
' FR-44: Notifications + Realtime Badge + Mark Read
' ============================================================

title **SD-17: Hệ thống Thông báo\n(Notification System)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E0F7FA
    ParticipantBorderColor #00838F
    ArrowColor #00838F
}

actor "User\n(any role)" as User
participant "Browser\n(JSP + JS)" as Browser #LightYellow
participant "NotificationServlet\n(API)" as Controller #E0F7FA
participant "NotificationService" as Service #E8F5E9
participant "NotificationDAO" as DAO #FFF3E0
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5

== Realtime Badge (AJAX Polling) ==

note over Browser
  JavaScript polling mỗi 10 giây
  để kiểm tra notification mới
end note

Browser -> Controller: GET /api/notifications/count\n(Cookie: JSESSIONID)
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: getUnreadCount(userId)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: countUnread(userId)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Notifications\nWHERE userId = ? AND isRead = 0
activate DB
DB --> DAO: count = 5
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: 5
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: 5
deactivate Service
Controller --> Browser: JSON {count: 5}
deactivate Controller
Browser -> Browser: Update badge: 🔔 (5)\non navbar notification icon

== Xem danh sách Notifications ==

User -> Browser: Click 🔔 icon
Browser -> Controller: GET /api/notifications\n?page=1&limit=20
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: getNotifications(\nuserId, page, limit)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: findByUser(userId, offset, limit)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM Notifications\nWHERE userId = ?\nORDER BY createdAt DESC\nOFFSET ? ROWS FETCH NEXT ? ROWS ONLY
activate DB
DB --> DAO: List<Notification>
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: notifications
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: notifications
deactivate Service
Controller --> Browser: JSON {notifications: [\n  {id, type, message,\n   isRead, createdAt,\n   relatedEventId, relatedOrderId}\n]}
deactivate Controller
Browser -> Browser: Render dropdown:\n- 🔴 "Sự kiện X đã được duyệt" (2m ago)\n- 🔴 "Đơn hàng đã thanh toán" (5m ago)\n- ⚪ "Tin nhắn mới từ BTC" (1h ago)

== Đánh dấu đã đọc ==

User -> Browser: Click vào notification
Browser -> Controller: POST /api/notifications/mark-read\n{notificationId}
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: markAsRead(notifId, userId)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: markRead(notifId)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: UPDATE Notifications SET\nisRead = 1,\nreadAt = GETDATE()\nWHERE notificationId = ?\nAND userId = ?
activate DB
DB --> DAO: Updated
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: OK
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: OK
deactivate Service
Controller --> Browser: JSON {success: true}
deactivate Controller
Browser -> Browser: Remove 🔴 indicator\nUpdate badge: 🔔 (4)

alt Notification has link
    Browser -> Browser: Navigate to related page:\n- EVENT_APPROVED → /organizer/events/{id}\n- ORDER_CONFIRMED → /tickets\n- NEW_CHAT → /chat/session/{id}\n- TICKET_RESPONSE → /support/{id}
end

== Đánh dấu tất cả đã đọc ==

User -> Browser: Click "Mark all as read"
Browser -> Controller: POST /api/notifications/mark-all-read
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: markAllAsRead(userId)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: markAllRead(userId)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: UPDATE Notifications SET\nisRead = 1, readAt = GETDATE()\nWHERE userId = ?\nAND isRead = 0
activate DB
DB --> DAO: N rows updated
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: OK
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: OK
deactivate Service
Controller --> Browser: JSON {success: true}
deactivate Controller
Browser -> Browser: Clear all 🔴 indicators\nBadge: 🔔 (0)

@enduml
